GG_MONUMENT (VERSION 1)

To install, extract to:

steam\steamapps\username\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

Included are the map (gg_monumentv1.bsp) and a nav mesh for bots (gg_monumentv1.nav).  Nav mesh isn't very good, but it's functional. (They like to get stuck on a couple of things, I didn't put much effort into it.)

This map is intended for Gun Game or Deathmatch. It isn't large, but I may expand it in the future. Version 2 will include a nice 3D skybox and possibly some underground passages.
